en_308932_0	60 Army personnel including 6 Officers volunteered to offer their blood to patients in Kilinochchi Hospital on Thursday (01) when the Bank of Ceylon Kilinochchi branch held a blood donation to mark its anniversary.
en_308932_1	The project was launched to mark the 80th BOC branch anniversary.
en_308932_2	To sustain goodwill between civilians and members of the Security Forces, the Commander, Security Forces - Kilinochchi, Major General Vijitha Ravipriya assured his support to the project.
